      "body": "@Rowandjj The deviceHeight gotten in `this.$getConfig()` is the real device height in pixel, not the height with 750-adapted.   \n\nSo you should convert it to a 750-adapted height:\n\n```\nvar screenHeight = 750 / config.env.deviceWidth * config.env.deviceHeight \n```\n\nThis may be a pretty inelegant way, but it can solve your problem.\n"
